  <entry>
    <title>docker中使用mysql做定时备份</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/01/14/devops/crontab-mysql-docker/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/01/14/devops/crontab-mysql-docker/</id>
    <published>2019-01-14T08:13:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-01-02T05:57:54.057Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1，写sh脚本,放在宿主机上的/shell下<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 保留10天数据，</span><br><span class="line"># mysqldocker 为安装mysql的docker</span><br><span class="line">docker exec -i mysql bash&lt;&lt;&apos;EOF&apos;</span><br><span class="line"># 判断目录是不是已经存在，如果不存在则创建</span><br><span class="line">if [ ! -d &quot;/backups/mysql&quot; ]; then</span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p /backups/mysql</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line"># ohstudydb 为数据库的名称</span><br><span class="line">mysqldump ohstudydb -uroot -p&apos;123456&apos; &gt; /backups/mysql/backups_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql</span><br><span class="line">#删除超过10天的数据</span><br><span class="line">rm -f /backups/mysql/backups_$(date -d -10day +%Y%m%d).sql</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br><span class="line">EOF</span><br><span class="line"># 判断目录是不是已经存在，如果不存在则创建</span><br><span class="line">if [ ! -d &quot;/backups/mysql&quot; ]; then</span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p /backups/mysql</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line"># 将docker中的备份的数据拷贝到宿主机上。</span><br><span class="line">docker cp mysql:/backups/mysql/backups_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql /backups/mysql</span><br><span class="line">#删除超过10天的数据</span><br><span class="line">rm -f /backups/mysql/backups_$(date -d -10day +%Y%m%d).sql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>注意：格式需要转换，在notepad中转换为 编辑-文档格式转换-Unix</p><p>完成后自定测试脚本是否正常运行</p><p>2，安装crontab<br>yum -y install vixie-cron<br>yum -y install crontabs</p><p>3，增加定时任务<br>crontab -e<br>1 0 <em> </em> * sh /shell/backups.sh 每天凌晨12点01分执行</p><p>补充：<br>日志位置：（待补充）</p>]]></content>
    
